data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***New Price Adjustment, Great Price for Bayshore Beautiful***    Welcome to South Tampa, 2 blocks from Bayshore Blvd !! This 4 bedroom 2 bath completely Solar home is in the heart of everything. Upon entering, your eyes will immediately catch the wonderful oak wood floors. There is a full living and dining room. The remodeled cook's kitchen has floor to ceiling cabinetry and stainless steel appliances. A gas range with griddle and undermount wine cooler are just some of the added benefits. Off the kitchen is a sun filled family room. The large secluded master suite has 2 walk-in closets. The en-suite master bath is trimmed out with a soaking tub, double sinks and large spa style shower with ceiling rain head. On the other side of the house can be found 3 additional bedrooms and a full bath. Both the family room and kitchen have entrances to the outdoor covered patio deck. This fenced yard area has multiple entertaining areas and is capped off by a detached 2 car garage at the rear of the property. The property went completely Solar last year with a monthly set cost of less than $150 a month. The property is also unique for South Tampa in that the 135 foot deep lot abounds Alline in the front and Asbury in the back for additional options. Quick Two block walk to famous  Bayshore Blvd on one of Tampa's beautiful antique brick streets, close to shopping, dining, and everything Tampa has to offer.
